createTime.description: Time when the row was created.

name.description: The resource name of the row. Row names have the form `tables/{table}/rows/{row}`. The name is ignored when creating a row.

updateTime.description: Time when the row was last updated.

values.description: The values of the row. This is a map of column key to value. Key is user entered name(default) or the internal column id based on the view in the request.

mappings.name: Lists rows in a table. Returns NOT_FOUND if the table does not exist.
